text: Emma Oudiou (born 2 January 1995) is a French athlete who competes in 3000 metre steeplechase events in international level events. She is a double bronze medalist in the European Athletics U23 Championships in this event. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Paris Category:French female steeplechase runners Category:French female middle-distance runners Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Mediterranean Games
